#: ../../S/spaghetti-inheritance.rst:5
msgid "spaghetti inheritance"
msgstr "spaghetti inheritance"

#: ../../S/spaghetti-inheritance.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../S/spaghetti-inheritance.rst:9
msgid ""
"[encountered among users of object-oriented languages that use inheritance, "
"such as Smalltalk] A convoluted class-subclass graph, often resulting from "
"carelessly deriving subclasses from other classes just for the sake of "
"reusing their code. Coined in a (successful) attempt to discourage such "
"practice, through guilt-by-association with :ref:`spaghetti-code`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Smalltalkのような、継承を使うオブジェクト指向言語のユーザーの間で見られる] "
"入り組んだクラス・サブクラスのグラフ。しばしば、ただコードを再利用するためだけに、他のクラスから不注意にサブクラスを派生させた結果生じる。\\ "
":ref:`spaghetti-code`\\ との連想による罪悪感を通じて、そうした慣行を思いとどまらせる(成功した)試みの中で作られた造語。"
